  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/c231c300373510aa297cfa9f5eefc0f8.avif?t=1773004615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras_big/c231c300373510aa297cfa9f5eefc0f8.avif?t=1773004615 width=800 height=483 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flora & Fang: Guardians of the vampire garden is a single-player or local co-op adventure that puts you in the shoes of one of two lovable vampire siblings, Flora or Fang, as they embark on a mission to safeguard their dad, the infamous Dracula's, precious pumpkin garden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/85e9719112ce4c11cb1626a336643b9c.poster.avif?t=1773004615\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/85e9719112ce4c11cb1626a336643b9c.webm?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/85e9719112ce4c11cb1626a336643b9c.mp4?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight the insect invasion!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spray, jump and pop the waves of pumpkin stealing insects! Armed with bug spray and a variety of traps and power-ups you repel waves of bothersome bugs in a variety of single screen stages. The vampire gardens future depends on you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play alone or with a friend!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/5d29bb00eda7710bdd2667c1f00fdced.poster.avif?t=1773004615\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/5d29bb00eda7710bdd2667c1f00fdced.webm?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/5d29bb00eda7710bdd2667c1f00fdced.mp4?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Place traps and upgrade your gear</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into the world of traps and strategy, where earning coins allows you to purchase clever, upgradeable traps that transform the game into a more defensive experience with light tower defense strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/c8175b67a7cae89c168c6cf0e102ed64.poster.avif?t=1773004615\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/c8175b67a7cae89c168c6cf0e102ed64.webm?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/c8175b67a7cae89c168c6cf0e102ed64.mp4?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Giant insect bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront larger-than-life insect bosses in thrilling boss battles that test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/def61092b76a558af3c59061bcbe19ea.poster.avif?t=1773004615\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/def61092b76a558af3c59061bcbe19ea.webm?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/def61092b76a558af3c59061bcbe19ea.mp4?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your father proud! Flora & Fang: Guardians of the vampire garden has</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 50 stages!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vampires!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradeable traps!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Insects!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Couch co-op!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sibling rivalry!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/c231c300373510aa297cfa9f5eefc0f8.avif?t=1773004615\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras_big/c231c300373510aa297cfa9f5eefc0f8.avif?t=1773004615 width=800 height=483 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flora & Fang: Guardians of the vampire garden is a single-player or local co-op adventure that puts you in the shoes of one of two lovable vampire siblings, Flora or Fang, as they embark on a mission to safeguard their dad, the infamous Dracula's, precious pumpkin garden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/85e9719112ce4c11cb1626a336643b9c.poster.avif?t=1773004615\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/85e9719112ce4c11cb1626a336643b9c.webm?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751060/extras/85e9719112ce4c11cb1626a336643b9c.mp4?t=1773004615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight the insect invasion!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spray, jump and pop the waves of pumpkin stealing insects! Armed with bug spray and a variety of traps and power-ups you repel waves of bothersome bugs in a variety of single screen stages. The vampire gardens future depends on you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play alone or with a friend!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loo